subtitleNullable: Electrcity Consumption and weather features for 3 Years
descriptionNullable:
The dataset comprises the energy consumption of a single student household in the Aarhus Municipality of Denmark, paired with meteorological features extracted from the Danish Meteorological Institut (DMI). 

The time period is 01.11.2018 to 01.11.2021. 

The following link offers a detailed description of the data context of the meteorological features by DMI:

https://confluence.govcloud.dk/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=26476616&fbclid=IwAR3IIvZ6_gABMYjlUJ4lwSZX545XY0DEKGIBxVj13utg8Wmuky5w-9DUyS8
